 bugs<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n1.(x)(a&gt;Rx)   p<br />\n2.(Ex)(a 。 Bx)   p<br />\n3.a。Bx   2.EI<br />\n4.a&gt;Rx    1. UI<br />\n5.a   3.Simp<br />\n6.Rx  4, 5 MP<br />\n7.Bx  3. Simp<br />\n8.Rx。Bx  6, 7 Conj<br />\n9.(Ex)(Rx。Bx)  8.EG<br />\n<br />\n所以，部分紅色水果有蟲蛀<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"567949c77d32c8647873a8fef23bc61941cfb4cc","tid":1005323,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65bb16e42c889ab569c290ba3c0a15a6257a5a23","tid":1005323,"uid":163972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"311a9d9613d421e3638faf16cc7d91ae8a416283","tid":1005323,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278f8b1d98acb6b49f504bee298138d26a523d17","tid":1005323,"uid":163972,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:14:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"錯，頭兩句有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尾三句只係重覆返個三段論論證<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1) 「紅色水果，不是所有都是蘋果」 唔係支持「所有蘋果都係紅色水果」嘅理由。<br />\n<br />\n試考慮紅色嘅士多啤梨。佢係紅色水果嘅一種，但仍然有可能「所有蘋果都係紅色水果」係假：有青蘋果。<br />\n<br />\n2) 「不是所有蘋果都有蟲蛀」唔係支持「部分蘋果嘅有蟲蛀」。<br />\n<br />\n當全部蘋果都有蟲蛀，「不是所有蘋果都有蟲蛀」係真，但「部分蘋果嘅有蟲蛀」都係假。"},{"pid":"2e3b53da2ff58e7b5e7e24a617d477dcf42810ab","tid":1005323,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>0岩即係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>錯，頭兩句有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尾三句只係重覆返個三段論論證<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1) 「紅色水果，不是所有都是蘋果」 唔係支持「所有蘋果都係紅色水果」嘅理由。<br />\n<br />\n試考慮紅色嘅士多啤梨。佢係紅色水果嘅一種，但仍然有可能「所有蘋果都係紅色水果」係假：有青蘋果。<br />\n<br />\n2) 「不是所有蘋果都有蟲蛀」唔係支持「部分蘋果嘅有蟲蛀」。<br />\n<br />\n當全部蘋果都<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有蟲蛀</span>，「不是所有蘋果都有蟲蛀」係真，但「部分蘋果嘅有蟲蛀」都係假。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b78e6c83f71afd12fe62f770c13b11930185d300","tid":1005323,"uid":163972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebbbbcc75e84862a7a20eaaa0a4ceedd3f80bc5e","tid":1005323,"uid":201158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:15:13.000Z","msg":"唔好上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4434407e999ff9524cb700669de2559a97b4f737","tid":1005323,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57f9c40a5dffbc9febd1874143872b1587c4ea2e","tid":1005323,"uid":139462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65bb16e42c889ab569c290ba3c0a15a6257a5a23","tid":1005323,"uid":163972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"311a9d9613d421e3638faf16cc7d91ae8a416283","tid":1005323,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"Domain: things<br />\na = apple<br />\nR = Red Fruits<br />\nB = have bugs<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n1.(x)(a&gt;Rx)   p<br />\n2.(Ex)(a 。 Bx)   p<br />\n3.a。Bx   2.EI<br />\n4.a&gt;Rx    1. UI<br />\n5.a   3.Simp<br />\n6.Rx  4, 5 MP<br />\n7.Bx  3. Simp<br />\n8.Rx。Bx  6, 7 Conj<br />\n9.(Ex)(Rx。Bx)  8.EG<br />\n<br />\n所以，部分紅色水果有蟲蛀<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"邏輯 可以分兩種方法 <br />\n一種就係 step-by-step, 好似natural deduction咁<br />\n根據規則，推演出下一步<br />\n但用 natural deduction 呢類方法 比較慢 <br />\n同埋往往要翻譯為符號 <br />\n如果連咁簡單嘅論證  都要搞到太複雜 <br />\n咁就邏輯就變相作為不大<br />\n<br />\n另一種方法，就係邏輯學叫 semantics，會比較快 同運用方法<br />\n唔講深入嘅細節，<br />\n運用呢種方法，主要係嘗試建立一種想前提皆為真，而結論為假」嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n要結論為假，即係要「所有紅色水果都沒有蟲蛀」 <br />\n所以，根據前提一，所有蘋果都沒有蟲柱 <br />\n但呢一點，同前提 2有矛盾 <br />\n所以唔會出現呢種情況，所以呢個論證有效"},{"pid":"d5e86b3cd400528378caaa3b029edd6748b8fbb6","tid":1005323,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78e6c83f71afd12fe62f770c13b11930185d300","tid":1005323,"uid":163972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e3b53da2ff58e7b5e7e24a617d477dcf42810ab","tid":1005323,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>0岩即係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>錯，頭兩句有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尾三句只係重覆返個三段論論證<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1) 「紅色水果，不是所有都是蘋果」 唔係支持「所有蘋果都係紅色水果」嘅理由。<br />\n<br />\n試考慮紅色嘅士多啤梨。佢係紅色水果嘅一種，但仍然有可能「所有蘋果都係紅色水果」係假：有青蘋果。<br />\n<br />\n2) 「不是所有蘋果都有蟲蛀」唔係支持「部分蘋果嘅有蟲蛀」。<br />\n<br />\n當全部蘋果都<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有蟲蛀</span>，「不是所有蘋果都有蟲蛀」係真，但「部分蘋果嘅有蟲蛀」都係假。</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:26:15.000Z","msg":"「所有蘋果都係紅色水果」 唔 imply「紅色水果不是所有都是蘋果」<br />\n「紅色水果不是所有都是蘋果」亦唔 imply 「所有蘋果都係紅色水果」<br />\n<br />\n你似乎將兩者混淆左"},{"pid":"4565805ee84c67b64c69e109f9bf7809158f00ed","tid":1005323,"uid":163972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a1a4efd0cba90b71abfd99dbba92c9c8d6da88f","tid":1005323,"uid":74462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ff730bd82b5985600a29ebf4581056bc4b7ae7","tid":1005323,"uid":74462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}